The [[Standard year/Legends|year]] '''4086 before the Battle of Yavin (BBY)''' was a period of [[Time/Legends|time]] during the [[Post-Manderon period|era]] between the [[Manderon Period]] and the [[Old Sith Wars]]. That year, the magazine ''[[Trampeta's Star Guide]]'' first began to be published.<ref name="NEGTD">''[[The New Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

